step_data.thought: I've successfully set up a route from Miami to Orlando using car transportation, and the system has calculated the route with a travel time of 6 hours and 38 minutes for a distance of 493km. Now I need to compare this with other transportation modes. Looking at the page, I can see a dropdown menu (combobox) with bid 166 that currently has 'Car (OSRM)' selected. To compare travel times, I should select another transportation mode like 'Bicycle (OSRM)' from this dropdown, then click 'Go' again to see the travel time for that mode. After collecting information for different modes, I can report the comparison to the user.
